casebody.data:
Jonathan LEWIS, petitioner,
v.
Howard FORMAN, Clerk, Circuit Court of Florida, Broward County. No. 13-5444. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013. Case below, 117 So.3d 411 .

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Florida dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
